      "content": "okay so if I do the 50k for a month like you said, what should i look out for? if i start feeling a bit nauseous or thirsty, should i just keep going through the month or is that a sign i should stop immediately? i'm really trying to make sure i don't mess this up since i really need the energy boost for work.",
